title: S13 Ep107: Traveling Realm of Death
itunes:title: Traveling Realm of Death
description:
Today on BEYOND the DARKNESS we are Traveling Realm of Death with our guest Cyrus Kirkpatrick..

What is it like to travel out of body and encounter the dead? Can we visit different planes of afterlife or are we forced by unseen rules to stay within certain boundaries? Cyrus walks us through some amazing first hand encounters and stories of strange encounters in the Astral Realm.

Cyrus Kirkpatrick is a metaphysical author, travel writer and truth-seeker.
Visit his site and get his books, here: http://afterlifetopics.com/

PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind!
